<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="fa" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>مجموعه تجاری پورشیخی</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vazirmatn:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Vazirmatn', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #e7dfd8, #d2c2b4);
      color: #3a312c;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }.logo {
  max-width: 130px;
  margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 2.6rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  color: #3a312c;
  text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  animation: slideIn 1s ease;
}

.tagline {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: #5e5147;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
}

.btn {
  display: block;
  width: 240px;
  margin: 1.2rem auto;
  padding: 1rem;
  border-radius: 12px;
  color: #3a312c;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e4d8ce, #f8f5f2);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(90, 70, 50, 0.2);
  border: 1px solid #b29f91;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.btn::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: -100%;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  transform: skewX(-20deg);
  transition: left 0.6s ease;
}

.btn:hover::before {
  left: 100%;
}

.btn:hover {
  background: #b29f91;
  color: #fff;
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.02);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(100, 80, 60, 0.4);
}

.branches {
  margin-top: 3rem;
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

.branch {
  background: #f8f5f2;
  border: 1px solid #e3dcd5;
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(60, 50, 40, 0.08);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  position: relative;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.branch:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(100, 80, 60, 0.25);
  transform: translateY(-3px);
}

.branch::before {
  content: '📍';
  position: absolute;
  left: 1.5rem;
  top: 1.2rem;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.branch-title {
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #3a312c;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes slideIn {
  from { transform: translateY(-20px); opacity: 0; }
  to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}

@media (max-width: 500px) {
  .btn {
    width: 90%;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .branch {
    padding: 1rem;
  }
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <img src="logo.png" alt="مجموعه تجاری پورشیخی" class="logo" />
  <h1>مجموعه تجاری پورشیخی</h1>
  <div class="tagline">مشتری مداری  ، کیفیت ، اصالت</div><a class="btn" href="https://instagram.com/poursheykhi.comm" target="_blank">صفحه اینستاگرام</a> <a class="btn" href="https://poursheykhi.com" target="_blank">وب‌سایت رسمی</a>

  <div class="branches">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #3a312c;">شعب ما</h2><div class="branch" onclick="window.open('https://goo.gl/maps/7QZAz1NHdWZbTb3t7','_blank')">
  <div class="branch-title">فروشگاه مرکزی 🏬</div>
  <div>اهواز، سیمتری نبش خیابان اهوازیان</div>
</div>

<div class="branch" onclick="window.open('https://goo.gl/maps/ZtuacvL3QzSVCmvz9','_blank')">
  <div class="branch-title">خانه تشک 🛏</div>
  <div>اهواز، سیمتری نبش خیابان اهوازیان</div>
</div>

<div class="branch" onclick="window.open('https://goo.gl/maps/ULzVrk7gyWWKX1TeA','_blank')">
  <div class="branch-title">پارک سنتر 🛍</div>
  <div>پارک سنتر، طبقه سوم، واحد ۳۱۹</div>
</div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
